name: Mouse Ears
description: These mouse ears are absolutely adorable and are sure to be a hit with your little girl. They are great for play time and are also a lot of fun for a birthday party. The head band the ears are attached to are designed to fit kids and adults. This allows adults to have some fun as well. :-)

name: Baby's First Christmas Tutu 6 to 9 Month Size
description: There is nothing more special than baby's first Christmas. This tutu is perfect for such a special occasion. It is already made and ready to ship. The tutu is attached to the onsey with snaps so it can be removed to allow you to wash the onesy. The tutu has an elastic waistband so it can be worn with any outfit and the waistband will expand 2-3 inches to allow her to wear it for quite some time. The tutu measures 7 inches long. The onesy is a brand new 6-9 months size. This is great for Christmas as well as your Christmas photos.

name: Empire Waist Christmas Tulle Dress - 3T to 5T
description:
Your princess is sure to be a big hit on Christmas day in this adorable empire waist Christmas dress. The dress is made from high quality tulle with black satin ribbon around the waist and a white feather boa around the top. This dress can be gently hand washed and I will send care instructions with each dress. 

=====
SIZES
=====

3T Chest 21 inches Length 20 inches

4T Chest 22 inches Length 22 inches

5T Chest 23 inches Length 24 inches


*** To ensure the best fit please send your child's chest measurement that you get by measuring right under her arms. The elastic will stretch 2-3 inches.

name: Pink Petti Tutu Newborn to 5T
description:
This pink petti tutu is sure to be a big hit. The tutu is made from pink tulle with light pink tulle tied to the end of each dark pink strip. These tutus are not made until the order has been received and will not be worn until your little princess puts it on. 

I have included a sizing chart below to help you decide on a size. For the best fit possible please take a measurement of your daughter's waist. The elastic waist band will stretch 2-3 inches which will allow your princess to wear this for quite some time.

This tutu can be gently hand washed and I will include care instructions with each order.

=====
SIZES
=====

0 - 3 months Waist 14-1/2 inches Length 6-7 inches

3 - 6 months Waist 15 inches Length 6-7 inches 

6 - 9 months Waist 16 inches Length 7-8 inches

12-24 months Waist 17 inches Length 8-9 inches

2T Waist 18 inches Length 9 - 10 inches

3T Waist 19 inches Length 9-10 inches

4T Waist 20 inches Length 10-12 inches

5T Waist 21 inches Length 10-12 inches

If you prefer to measure your child's waist for a more exact fit please include that measurement when you order. Other sizes available on request.

name: Candy Cane Tulle Dress Size 3T-5T
description: This Candy Cane dress is as cute as it gets. The dress is made from high quality red and white tulle with red satin ribbon around the waist. A Poinsettia in the center of the ribbon completes the dress. The dress is tied with red tulle around your child's neck. This dress can be gently hand washed and I will send care instructions with each dress.
